#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an4.79"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.79:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.79:0.2"
msgid "8. Apaṇṇakavagga "
msgstr "8. Guaranteed "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: vaṇijjāsuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an4.79:0.3"
msgid "79. Vaṇijjasutta "
msgstr "79. Business "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an4.79:1.1"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā sāriputto yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā sāriputto bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then Venerable Sāriputta went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, and said to him: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.79:1.2"
msgid "“ko nu kho, bhante, hetu ko paccayo, yena midhekaccassa tādisāva vaṇijjā payuttā chedagāminī hoti? "
msgstr "“Sir, what is the cause, what is the reason why for different people the same kind of business undertaking might fail, "

#. VAR: yathādhippāyā → yathādhippāyaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an4.79:1.3"
msgid "Ko pana, bhante, hetu ko paccayo, yena midhekaccassa tādisāva vaṇijjā payuttā na yathādhippāyā hoti? "
msgstr "while another doesn’t meet expectations, "

#. VAR: yathādhippāyā → yathādhippāyaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an4.79:1.4"
msgid "Ko nu kho, bhante, hetu ko paccayo, yena midhekaccassa tādisāva vaṇijjā payuttā yathādhippāyā hoti? "
msgstr "another meets expectations, "

msgctxt "an4.79:1.5"
msgid "Ko pana, bhante, hetu ko paccayo, yena midhekaccassa tādisāva vaṇijjā payuttā parādhippāyā hotī”ti? "
msgstr "and another exceeds expectations?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.82, sc2
msgctxt "an4.79:2.1"
msgid "“Idha, sāriputta, ekacco samaṇaṃ vā brāhmaṇaṃ vā upasaṅkamitvā pavāreti: ‘vadatu, bhante, paccayenā’ti. So yena pavāreti taṃ na deti. "
msgstr "“Sāriputta, take a case where someone goes to an ascetic or brahmin and invites them to ask for what they need. But they fail to give what’s requested. "

msgctxt "an4.79:2.2"
msgid "So ce tato cuto itthattaṃ āgacchati, so yaññadeva vaṇijjaṃ payojeti, sāssa hoti chedagāminī. "
msgstr "When they’ve passed away from that life, if they’re reborn in this state of existence, whatever business they undertake fails. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an4.79:3.1"
msgid "Idha pana, sāriputta, ekacco samaṇaṃ vā brāhmaṇaṃ vā upasaṅkamitvā pavāreti: ‘vadatu, bhante, paccayenā’ti. So yena pavāreti taṃ na yathādhippāyaṃ deti. "
msgstr "Take a case where someone goes to an ascetic or brahmin and invites them to ask for what they need. They give what’s requested, but don’t meet expectations. "

#. VAR: yathādhippāyā → yathādhippāyaṃ (bj, mr)
msgctxt "an4.79:3.2"
msgid "So ce tato cuto itthattaṃ āgacchati, so yaññadeva vaṇijjaṃ payojeti, sāssa na hoti yathādhippāyā. "
msgstr "When they’ve passed away from that life, if they’re reborn in this state of existence, whatever business they undertake doesn’t meet expectations. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "an4.79:4.1"
msgid "Idha pana, sāriputta, ekacco samaṇaṃ vā brāhmaṇaṃ vā upasaṅkamitvā pavāreti: ‘vadatu, bhante, paccayenā’ti. So yena pavāreti taṃ yathādhippāyaṃ deti. "
msgstr "Take a case where someone goes to an ascetic or brahmin and invites them to ask for what they need. They give what’s requested, meeting expectations. "

#. VAR: yathādhippāyā → yathādhippāyaṃ (bj, mr)
msgctxt "an4.79:4.2"
msgid "So ce tato cuto itthattaṃ āgacchati, so yaññadeva vaṇijjaṃ payojeti, sāssa hoti yathādhippāyā. "
msgstr "When they’ve passed away from that life, if they’re reborn in this state of existence, whatever business they undertake meets expectations. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "an4.79:5.1"
msgid "Idha, sāriputta, ekacco samaṇaṃ vā brāhmaṇaṃ vā upasaṅkamitvā pavāreti: ‘vadatu, bhante, paccayenā’ti. So yena pavāreti taṃ parādhippāyaṃ deti. "
msgstr "Take a case where someone goes to an ascetic or brahmin and invites them to ask for what they need. They give what’s requested, exceeding expectations. "

#. VAR: parādhippāyā → parādhippāyaṃ (si, mr)
msgctxt "an4.79:5.2"
msgid "So ce tato cuto itthattaṃ āgacchati, so yaññadeva vaṇijjaṃ payojeti, sāssa hoti parādhippāyā. "
msgstr "When they’ve passed away from that life, if they’re reborn in this state of existence, whatever business they undertake exceeds expectations. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "an4.79:6.1"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho, sāriputta, hetu ayaṃ paccayo, yena midhekaccassa tādisāva vaṇijjā payuttā chedagāminī hoti. "
msgstr "This is the cause, this is the reason why for different people the same kind of business enterprise might fail, "

msgctxt "an4.79:6.2"
msgid "Ayaṃ pana, sāriputta, hetu ayaṃ paccayo, yena midhekaccassa tādisāva vaṇijjā payuttā na yathādhippāyā hoti. "
msgstr "while another doesn’t meet expectations, "

msgctxt "an4.79:6.3"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho pana, sāriputta, hetu ayaṃ paccayo, yena midhekaccassa tādisāva vaṇijjā payuttā yathādhippāyā hoti. "
msgstr "another meets expectations, "

msgctxt "an4.79:6.4"
msgid "Ayaṃ pana, sāriputta, hetu ayaṃ paccayo, yena midhekaccassa tādisāva vaṇijjā payuttā parādhippāyā hotī”ti. "
msgstr "and another exceeds expectations.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.79:6.5"
msgid "Navamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
